{
  "stem": "24462.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My haftarah was from Amos, [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH], and so on, and so on, so on, so on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Yes, my friends didn't come to my bar mitzvah because they were only late invited.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was some, some, some misunderstanding.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And no one from my friends-- only the family was there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "For my bar mitzvah I remember I brought from somewhere a [INAUDIBLE], which you call today disc player.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then I-- first time, I heard the music of Ketelbey, 'In the Chinese Garden,' and the 'Persian Market' of Ketelbey.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And what else-- and some other of the very well-known operas.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I had maybe a dozen, dozen records with the tube.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I was listening to the music.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then I probably-- I had it for a longer time or so.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But still, I was first time introduced to this music.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because we didn't have a radio, not speaking about television.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The first radio I got when I was 16 after a long, long talk with my father.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We bought a secondhand radio, old fashioned Phillips, this shape.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was operating this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I-- long wires to my bed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then I knew how to find the short waves, and the medium, and so on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I, I enjoyed the radio very, very much, especially during the Olympics.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "During the Olympics in '36, in Germany, every day it was a communique about what happened, and Jesse Owens-- and you know Jesse Owens-- and so on, and so on.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So the radio was very, very useful.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This is the first time I had a radio.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And well, I was using it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, but they are typical Polish programs, comedy things and-- which I, I don't, I don't recall very well.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
